high_descs: Go to the counter to the right of the fridge
Grab the knife off of the counter
Move slightly to the right
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices
Put the knife down on the counter
Grab a slice of tomato
Move slightly to the right and face the microwave
Heat the tomato in the microwave and then take it out
Turn around and go to the small black table
Put the tomato on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a sliced tomato on the black table

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the counter between the refrigerator and the stove.
Pick up the knife under the spoon and to the left of the salt, on the counter.
Move over to your right so that you are in front of the tomato, on the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Place the knife back on the counter, on the right side of the salt.
Pick up one of the tomato slices, on the counter.
Move over to your right so that you are in front of the stove.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave, above the stove, heat it up, the remove the tomato slice from the microwave.
Turn around and walk across to kitchen, then when you reach the end, turn right and go to the small, black table in the left corner.
Put the tomato slice on the front, right corner of the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato slice on the table.

high_descs: Go over to the counter on the left side of the stove and face it.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Look to the right of the counter.
Use the knife to slice the red pepper.
Put the knife back down on the counter.
Pick up a piece of the sliced pepper.
Bring the pepper with you, take a step to the right, and then look up at the microwave.
Put the pepper in the microwave and cook it, then take it out again.
Bring the pepper with you across the room, then turn right and face the small black table.
Put the pepper down on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put some warm pepper on the table.
